OL,3,CAlcohol consumption falling, drinks
OL,4,Cindustry says
OL,6,FAlcohol consumption in Ireland is down
OL,7,Fby almost one-third in the past two
OL,8,Fdecades, according to a study.
OL,10,FAverage alcohol consumption continues
OL,11,Fto fall based on CSO population
OL,12,Ffigures and Revenue alcohol clearance
OL,13,Fdata.
OL,15,FBeer accounts for 42.9% of the alcohol
OL,16,Fmarket in Ireland, according to the
OL,17,Freport authored by economist and
OL,18,Fassociate professor emeritus at DCU
OL,19,FAnthony Foley.
